        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2420531035" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3271462517769886242">My partner and I call this book our &quot;food bible&quot;. I have learned so much valuable information about food, how to cook it, and what to buy. If you want to learn how to make food that is simple and delicious, I highly recommend this cookbook. It&apos;s also a fantastic tool for developing a skillset since Waters gives detailed explanations on how to cook certain staples. </span>
  <span id="freeText3271462517769886242" style="display:none">My partner and I call this book our "food bible". I have learned so much valuable information about food, how to cook it, and what to buy. If you want to learn how to make food that is simple and delicious, I highly recommend this cookbook. It's also a fantastic tool for developing a skillset since Waters gives detailed explanations on how to cook certain staples. </span>
